  32:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****   [..] The FLASH main features are:
  33:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Flash memory read operations
  34:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Flash memory program/erase operations
  35:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Read / write protections
