  38:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Watermark-based area protection
  39:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Block-based sector protection
  40:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Error code correction (ECC)
