  73:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Set the latency
  74:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Enable/Disable the FLASH interrupts
  75:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Monitor the FLASH flags status
  76:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****      [..]
  77:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_flash.c ****     (@) The contents of the Flash memory are not guaranteed if a device reset occurs during
